ers involving regulatory authorities, including responding to inquiries, preparing for audits, and challenging fines or penalties. Our experienced attorneys work closely with clients to navigate regulatory investigations and minimize legal and financial exposure.\\n\"}]}', '2024-09-13 01:09:00', 'data-protection-law');
